'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2310] on 12 June 2000 at 2:32:24 pm'!"Change Set:		149ValueWithRec-smaDate:			12 June 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustAs discussed in the list, a way to call a compiled method directly."!!CompiledMethod methodsFor: 'evaluating' stamp: 'sma 6/12/2000 14:29'!valueWithReceiver: aReceiver arguments: anArray 	| selector |	selector _ Symbol new.	aReceiver class addSelector: selector withMethod: self.	^ [aReceiver perform: selector withArguments: anArray]		ensure: [aReceiver class removeSelectorSimply: selector]! !